sec.p: Three analyzes were done to identify the differential components in the three oils. Analyze 1 (Anlz1) referred to the oils extracted in 2013 and analyzed in 2014. The oils samples were re-analyzed in 2016, mentioned as Analyze 2 (Anlz2), in order to study the stability of the components. The third one (Anlz3) referred to samples extracted in 2015 and analyzed in 2016.
